name: PKTransitPassProperties
desc: The properties of a transit pass.

items.name: var expirationDate: Date?
items.desc: The date that the transit card expires.

items.name: var isInStation: Bool
items.desc: A Boolean value that indicates whether the transit pass has tapped in at a station and has not tapped out.

items.name: var isBlocked: Bool
items.desc: A Boolean value that indicates the pass issuer disabled the pass.
